<br>
Basically, you can now alt-tab out of the game and back just like in beta.<br>
<br>
Interesting question: is using this program "cheating"?  You derive no in-game advantage from it's use.  You are not invulnerable when you use it.  It doesn't actually affect anything in the game at all.<br>
